		dependencies: ["0000000000230004"]
		title: "Tier 3: Speed Runes"
		icon: {id: "bloodmagic:apprentice_blood_orb", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Speed Runes (Acceleration Runes) reduce the altar's crafting time dramatically. Add enough to push to Tier 3 and the altar becomes fast enough for Living Armor and ritual component recipes.", "T3 also unlocks the Apprentice Blood Orb, which holds 25,000 LP. Your Soul Network just got a lot deeper."]
