		title: "The Ritual Diviner"
		icon: {id: "bloodmagic:ritual_diviner", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Rituals are large multiblock structures built from Ritual Stones arranged around a Master Ritual Stone. The Ritual Diviner shows you exactly where each stone goes — right-click the ground and it projects the layout.", "There are rituals for crop growth, LP transfer across dimensions, mob summoning, and more. The Diviner is how you build them without losing your mind."]
