		x: 16.0d
		y: 2.0d
		dependencies: ["0000000000230010"]
		title: "Master Blood Orb"
		icon: {id: "bloodmagic:master_blood_orb", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Master Blood Orb holds 10 million LP — enough to sustain any ritual, any Living Armor build, and still have reserves. Reaching T5 altar means you've climbed the Capacity Rune ladder all the way up.", "At this point, Blood Magic stops gating you on LP quantity and starts gating you on ritual complexity. Everything from here is about what you build with your network, not how big it is."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000230017"
