		title: "Iesnium: Otherworld Metal"
		icon: {id: "occultism:iesnium_ingot", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Iesnium is Occultism's native metal, found only in the Otherworld dimension. You can reach it via a sacrificial ritual, or harvest it passively by binding a Djinn miner to a Dimensional Mineshaft.", "Iesnium is required for Spirit Attuned Pickaxe Heads, higher-tier Books of Binding, and the more powerful storage infrastructure. Get a supply running early."]
