		y: -2.0d
		dependencies: ["0000000000230019"]
		title: "Gold Chalk: Djinn Tier"
		icon: {id: "occultism:chalk_gold", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Gold Chalk is required for higher-rank rituals including Djinn summoning. Djinn are more versatile than Foliots: they can run Wild Crushers for ore doubling, power the Storage Actuator, and manage more demanding tasks.", "Craft the Gold Chalk, draw the summoning circle from the Dictionary of Spirits, place the ritual items, activate. The chalk is consumed. The Djinn is not."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "000000000023001D"
			type: "item"
