		x: 12.0d
		y: -2.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000023001C"]
		title: "Purple Chalk: Afrit Tier"
		icon: {id: "occultism:chalk_purple", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Afrit are third-rank demons. They're powerful enough to operate smelters, run machines Djinn can't handle, and manage weather-altering rituals. Purple Chalk unlocks their summoning circles.", "Getting an Afrit requires more materials and a larger ritual setup than a Djinn. The payoff is automation that would otherwise need much heavier infrastructure."]
