		y: -2.0d
		dependencies: ["000000000023001F"]
		title: "Dimensional Mineshaft"
		icon: {id: "occultism:dimensional_mineshaft", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Dimensional Mineshaft connects to a pocket dimension full of ore. Bind a Djinn miner to it and it will continuously extract ore from that dimension without touching your world.", "It doesn't run out. The pocket dimension regenerates. This is Occultism's passive ore generation — quiet, consistent, and completely hands-off once set up."]
