		title: "Marid: The Apex Rank"
		icon: {id: "occultism:chalk_red", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Marid are the most powerful demon rank in Occultism. Red Chalk is required for their circles. A bound Marid can perform tasks no lower rank can — cutting entire forests, mining deep veins, pulling resources from the deep Otherworld.", "Getting here means you've climbed all four ranks of the demonic hierarchy. Occultism at its peak is a silent army of bound spirits working while you do something else."]
