		dependencies: ["000000000000E024"]
		title: "Spirit Fire"
		icon: {id: "occultism:spirit_fire", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Spirit Fire is a special ritual flame that converts mundane materials into Otherworld components — logs to Otherwood, stone to Otherstone. It's created through a specific item ritual using candles and Otherstone.", "Spirit Fire conversions are how you mass-produce Otherworld materials without constantly farming Otherworld Trees. Once you have a source of logs and stone, you have infinite Otherworld materials."]
