		title: "The Familiar"
		icon: {id: "occultism:familiar_ring", Count: 1b}
		description: ["The Familiar ritual summons a spirit companion that bonds to you. Familiars provide passive buffs — a bat gives night vision, a cthulhu familiar gives water breathing, a beaver boosts mining speed. Equip the Familiar Ring in your curio slot so the familiar can follow you.", "Different familiars come from different ritual patterns. Check the Dictionary of Spirits for the circle matching the familiar you want."]
